    <description>This extension changes the way that the pricing of configurable products works in Magento. With this extension the price for configurable products is taken directly from the associated simple products rather than the configurable product itself.

This gives site owners direct control over the price of every individual configuration of a product, while still giving users the flexibility they usually get with configurable products. (There's no more having to set rules such as: +20% for blue, -&#xA3;10 for small, +15% for leather. You just price the underlying small-blue-leather product at &#xA3;199.99 and that's what the user pays.)

v0.7 has full support for: Special Prices, Tier Prices, Custom Options, Catalog Price Rules, dynamic changing of product image/description/name to match the matching associated product, etc

See http://github.com/organicinternet/magento-configurable-simple/ for installation and upgrade instructions and the complete feature list.

